# Script 6: Traffic Signals & Air Quality
# Display traffic light signal timing and phases
# Show air quality index and pollution hotspots
# Integrate signal uncertainty into routing decisions

# Load traffic signal data
signals load from OSM
  traffic signal locations
  cycle times (EU standard 45-90s)
  phases (red, green, yellow)

# Show signal information
show signal locations as points
show cycle time labels
show current phases with colors
  red = [255, 0, 0]
  yellow = [255, 255, 0]
  green = [0, 255, 0]

# Load air quality data
air quality load
  PM2.5 concentration
  NO2 levels
  CO levels
  AQI index

# Visualize air quality
show air quality heatmap
show pollution hotspots
show wind dispersion patterns

# Signal-routing integration
signal cycle time affects walking time
signal phase uncertainty = cycle time
resolution floor beta_0 = min(cycle time)

# Display results
signals report
air quality report
pollution zones show
